---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

// Hämta lang från URL:en
const { lang } = Astro.params;
---

<Layout title="About Us" lang={lang}>
  <main style="padding: 2rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>Welcome to <strong>vertoq.net</strong>, your go-to destination for fast, reliable, and user-friendly digital tools.</p>
    <p>We understand that modern digital tasks should be simple and efficient. That is why we have created a suite of tools designed to streamline your daily workflow—whether you are working on professional projects, student assignments, or everyday calculations. Our goal is to provide a clean, distraction-free environment where you can get the job done quickly and accurately.</p>
    <p><strong>vertoq.net</strong> is built with a focus on simplicity, speed, and accessibility. We are constantly improving and adding new features to ensure our tools meet the needs of our global community.</p>
    <p>Thank you for making us a part of your daily routine!</p>
  </main>
</Layout>